==English==
===Adjective===
'''responsible''' (more responsible, most responsible)
# [[legally]] [[answerable]]
#:''A parent is '''responsible''' for his child's behaviour.''
# involving [[personal]] [[accountability]] and [[decision]] [[making]]
#:''She has a '''responsible''' position in the firm.''
# being a [[cause]] of some event
#:''Who is '''responsible''' for this mess?''
# [[able]] to be [[trusted]]; [[reliable]]

